{"tid":1504653,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"容許我講一句","createTime":"2019-08-25T11:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T11:59:41.000Z","uid":37146,"like":7,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d5577956c257f927168c46bdc0db5769ae187766","tid":1504653,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:12:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">班前線真係蠢撚過豬！</span></span><br />\n又唔衝，又唔撤，又唔反攻<br />\n做個乖寶寶係現場等狗衝，乖乖拉到返去狗屋<br />\n男既俾狗打，女既俾狗屌<br />\n其實你地可唔可以至少保持一個目標就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不被捕！</span></span><br />\n你過衝唔到，攻唔到，但你可以走，唔好俾對家捉返去，咁玩法，只有軍心愈來愈低落<br />\n唉，你走，唔等於你輸，來日方長，慢慢玩，你被捉，入到去俾狗玩到下次你都唔敢出，咁就冇下次報仇機會<br />\n<br />\n香港人依家面對緊既係極無恥極醜惡既政府，唔好作無謂嘅犧牲，要留返戰力慢慢同佢玩，今次唔得，等下次，求下你地唔好再俾啲死賤種狗捉返去"},{"pid":"a03bd55c1b6331d8c3507b9a60610f48cea2e3ae","tid":1504653,"uid":264314,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"e626d0b49f86d2acb0fed3dae2eb57005251a0c6","tid":1504653,"uid":37146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:19:23.000Z","msg":"佩服所有前線既勇氣，同時希望你地珍惜呢份勇氣，唔好再犧牲<br />\n今日呢個環境咁不利，應該要走"},{"pid":"aea47beb2d1c6f4ecdeef2ad4550ded4ca173585","tid":1504653,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:22:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警死全家！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b853ac06926ca05f04626b93b3b9ec009b3277fd","tid":1504653,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:29:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警死全族！</span></span>"},{"pid":"34dcc16ae4d92d5b7e1ce32ec389bff4ab388c6c","tid":1504653,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"無講錯<br />\n不過香港人永遠都行唔出comfort zone<br />\n無人行先就知個坐係度望<br />\n又唔甘心乜都做唔到就撒，呢種心態會死人的"},{"pid":"fc669cc2a490001ee63c94579dd6a528e48d335c","tid":1504653,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:36:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,待定, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有機9月6(五)搞埋</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全部1點，唯一底線，唔衝禁區(會變恐襲)</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後既每個星期六/日 要起碼有一日一定係機場，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜撚都要讓路!!</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n國泰城改左828 (三)，被炒機師空姐需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19d3980732aa85cb407a6188dccb68ca63a406c","tid":1504653,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:41:37.000Z","msg":"香港人，一個都不能再少！<br />\n勇和都係咁重要！"},{"pid":"9ad2d01b356b7257eda6fc73ef2f1d850beee0c3","tid":1504653,"uid":44606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:42:00.000Z","msg":"講真 一係直接燒狗啦 成班前線出黎咩計劃都冇 比你full gear都唔燒狗"},{"pid":"1063587f9a5db665fce05f897cd4aaa64e46e341","tid":1504653,"uid":44606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:44:12.000Z","msg":"都玩得火魔法 燒碌燈柱有乜用"},{"pid":"6a44b3b84abd7e3f6da70c94522bd0e5f9b9d0ff","tid":1504653,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:59:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警絕子絕孫</span></span>"}]}